data.revised_prompt: Generate an abstract avatar icon featuring a warm glowing orb against a dark background. The orb should exude the hue of amber and honey and contain subtle internal patterns reminiscent of neural networks. The core of the orb should pulse with slightly more intensity, giving the illusion that it is alive, attentive, and present. The design should be minimalist, suitable for a profile picture and contain no face or text. The medium should be digital art.
